<div class='sfContentBlock'>With the steady increase in osteopathic medical school graduates, federal GME funding is critical to ensure the stability and continuity of medical residency training programs in the United States.


</div><div class='sfContentBlock  moreLink'><a href="http://cqrcengage.com/aacom/graduate_medical_education">Learn More</a>&nbsp;<em class="fa fa-angle-right fa-lg"></em>


</div></div></div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="threecol2">  <div class="tcwrap"><div class="tctop">
<div class='sfContentBlock'>Medical Student Debt


</div></div><div class="tcmid">
<div class='sfContentBlock'><a href="http://cqrcengage.com/aacom/student_financial_aid" target="_blank">Medical Student Debt</a>


</div></div><div class="tcbtm"><div class="tcbtmpad">
<div class='sfContentBlock'>AACOM recognizes the significant student loan debt burden osteopathic medical students and graduates shoulder, and encourages Congress to explore fiscally responsible solutions to lower medical student debt.


</div><div class='sfContentBlock  moreLink'><a href="http://cqrcengage.com/aacom/student_financial_aid">Learn More</a>&nbsp;<em class="fa fa-angle-right fa-lg"></em>


</div></div></div></div></div>
<div class="threecol3">  <div class="tcwrap"><div class="tctop">
<div class='sfContentBlock'>Physician Workforce


</div></div><div class="tcmid">
<div class='sfContentBlock'><a href="http://cqrcengage.com/aacom/primary_care_workforce" target="_blank">Physician Workforce</a>


</div></div><div class="tcbtm"><div class="tcbtmpad">
<div class='sfContentBlock'>The U.S. is confronting a primary care physician workforce shortage caused, in part, by population growth and aging. AACOM advocates for federal workforce and training programs that address this shortage.


</div><div class='sfContentBlock  moreLink'><a href="http://cqrcengage.com/aacom/primary_care_workforce">Learn More</a>&nbsp;<em class="fa fa-angle-right fa-lg"></em>
